			<div type="section" xml:id="Ch2.S2" n="22">
				<pb type="VIII_1" n="30"/>
				<head>2<hi rendition="#sub">2</hi>. INSTRUMENTUM LONGITUDINUM</head>
				<div type="ueberlieferung">
					<p><hi rendition="#b #smaller">Überlieferung:</hi><listWit>
						<witness><msDesc>
							<msIdentifier>
								<repository>Gottfried Wilhelm Leibniz Bibliothek Hannover</repository>
								<idno type="Signatur">XXX</idno>
							</msIdentifier>
							<msContents>
								<summary><p>Konzept: LH XXXV 15, 6 Bl. 46, 74. 1 Bog. 2<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>. 3/4 S. auf Bl. 74 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>. Linke Spalte mit Ausnahme der oberen 8 Zeilen unser Text. Zu den verbleibenden Seiten vgl. N. 2<!--  \hack{\raisebox{-0.5ex}{\tiny{1}}} 
     \hackfor{\textsubscript{1}}--><hi rendition="#sub">1</hi>. Geringe Textverluste am unteren Rand durch Papierabbruch.</p><p>KK 1, Nr. 193 B</p></summary>
							</msContents>
							<physDesc>
								<objectDesc form="Handschrift" corresp="L_objectDesc.xml#handschrift"/>
							</physDesc>
							<history>
								<origin/>
							</history>
							</msDesc></witness>
						</listWit></p>
				</div>
				<div type="text">
					<p xml:id="Ch2.S2.p4"><pb type="L"/><fw type="folNum">[74 v<hi rendition="#sup">o</hi>]</fw> Instrumentum Longitudinum<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>longitudo</term>
						</index> breviter tale esto: Fiat rotula aus trat, illius pennae sint ex subtilissimo blech. Incurvato aliquantum, ut ventum scilicet aerem tanto melius sinu quasi velum excipiat. Haec rotula in capsam angustam collocetur, ita ut aer in ea se diffundere non possit, et non plus spatii contineat fere, quam rota occupat. Sit aditus aeri ab una et exitus ab altera directe opposita parte, ita ut pennarum summitates sint in linea recta intus initum et exitum. Porro qua aditus aeri esse debet, fit <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">tubus sinum extro versus</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">fit</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> exterius </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> tubus sinum extro versus <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> late expandens, interius in acumen desinens multis modis flexum et incurvatum. Exitus sinum introrsus, acumen extrorsum pandat, flexione illi non opus <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">dummodo</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">opus</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> nec </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> dummodo <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> sit, quod a vento illabente pertegat. Esto etiam <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main"/>
						<rdg wit="#L" cause="deletion">etiam <note type="editorial">|</note> <del>ita</del> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">gestr.</hi> |</note> versum <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app>versum deorsum exeuntis acumen, ut protectum nihil impediat exitum. Haec capsula ponatur in loco aeri exposito, v.g. infigatur stylo, wie ein wetterhahn. Porro Rotam<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> axis, sed cum rota<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> mobilis transeat, et eam <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">in una parte capsulae incumbentem faciat</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">eam</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> affigat </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> in <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> faciat <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app>, sic tamen ut motus circa axem maneat liber. Iste axis sit tenuissima acicula. Ea ex altera parte porrigatur extra capsulam non incumbens, nisi in <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">loco extra capsulam post alteram</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">in</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> altero </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> loco extra capsulam post alteram <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> rotam. Extra capsulam ergo similem prorsus rotam<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> contineat, sed quo levior sit, eo discrimine, quod pinnis tam grandibus non opus, imo pro pinnis servient aciculae sibi conjuncte triquetrice hac forma, eminentes <formula xml:id="Ch2.S2.p4.m1">
						<m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline">
							<m:mo>△</m:mo>
						</m:math>
						</formula>. Porro <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">illa rota sit inter duos parietes</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">Porro</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> illi rotae<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
							<term>rota</term>
							</index> super incumbat </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> illa <seg type="apparat-ellipsis"/> parietes <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app>, in altero averso axis ejus cum priore communis, mobilis, sit firmatus, super Rotam hanc 2<hi rendition="#sup">dam</hi> sit linea longa aus eisentrat, continuis sinulis similis et distantiae eminentiis, instar serrae, ut rota<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> secunda. Haec linea <pb type="VIII_1" n="31"/>praeterea habeat unam longam aciculam descendentem. Porro haec linea quovis quadrante horae demittatur a portatoribus rigidis <graphic xml:id="Ch2.S2.p4.g1" url="../images/74vIL.svg" width="17.3448pt"/> duobus, quorum lineae rigidae incedant intra incisuras in pariete utroque, et descendant infra rotam<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index>, et lineam serratam relinquant in rota<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> ab ea propellendam, postea tanto tempore, quanto sinet <app type="Bfootnote">
						<!--is-correction-app-with-lemma-->
						<lem type="main"><corr resp="#ed">[quater]</corr></lem>
						<rdg wit="#L"><orig>quatuor</orig>  <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">L ändert Hrsg.</hi></note> </rdg>
						</app> quadrans ibi relinquentes resurgant rursus et reattollant. Post ultimum quadrantem <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">horae</lem>
						<rdg wit="#L" cause="addition"><add>horae</add> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">erg. L</hi></note></rdg>
						</app>, postquam resublata fuerit linea serrata haec contingat. Sit in linea serrata ea longa acus<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>acus</term>
						</index> non firmata sed supra eam in alia parallela linea aus trat simili simplice. Dum igitur propellitur a rota<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> secunda linea serrata, propellitur simul et simplex superius parallela, quippe quia acu connexae sunt. Postquam vero a quadrante ultimo relevata sit linea serrata <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">(acicula</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">(</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" cause="deletion"> <note type="editorial">|</note> <del>nam</del> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">gestr.</hi> |</note> acicula <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> cum ea non descendit) tunc superius malleoli duo utrinque a latere utroque hypomochlii (hypomochlium autem habebit foramen ut per <app type="Bfootnote">
						<!--is-correction-app-with-future-lemma-->
						<lem type="main"><corr resp="#ed">[id]</corr></lem>
						<rdg wit="#L"><orig>eam </orig>  <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">L ändert Hrsg.</hi></note> </rdg>
						</app> libere transire <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">possit</lem>
						<rdg wit="#L" cause="addition"><add>possit</add> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">erg. L</hi></note></rdg>
						</app>, et sit tale ut ad mallei ictum cedat et ipsum, et descendat aliquantulum) pulsent lineam simplicem, et ita descendet acus, et pulsabit inferius chartam, et ei foramen imprimet. Charta inferius subjecta sit <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">sed</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">sit</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> loco </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> sed <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> sic ut sub rotam<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>rota</term>
						</index> directe non veniat. Sit autem <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main"/>
						<rdg wit="#L" cause="deletion">autem <note type="editorial">|</note> <del>v.g.</del> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">gestr.</hi> |</note> der <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app>der Ramen, darein der papyr komt compactus ex aciculis ferreis, et latus septentrionale habent eminentes plurimas aciculas omnes fortiter polo<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>polus</term>
						</index> magnetis<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>magnes</term>
						</index> versus arcton inclinaturo affrictas, oppositae opposito. De caetero latera quasi caudicata quatuor circuitus linearum conjungantur similibus subtilissimis aciculis cum fulcro cui incumbunt. Fulcrum sit acies similiter tenuis wie im compas<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>Kompass</term>
						</index> descendens inferius ita ut neque sursum neque deorsum moveri, libere tamen circumagi possit. Quod facile praestitu. <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">Jam in</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">praestitu.</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> Ea ratione in </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Jam in <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> 4 angulis des Ramens emineant sursum aciculae, his infigatur charta firma, sed levis. Jam charta cum ramen semper se collocabit in situm ad polos<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>polus</term>
						</index>, quomodocunque vertatur navis<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>navis</term>
						</index>. Et ita impressione aciculae superioris <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">progredientis</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">superioris</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> et ea </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> progredientis <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> perfecte tum celeritas<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>celeritas</term>
						</index> tum flexio navis<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>navis</term>
						</index> apparebit. Uno ergo nondum explicatum horologium<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>horologium</term>
						</index>, quod quovis quadrante demittat et attollat portatores et quavis hora malleolo percutiat lineam simplicem. Quod cuivis artifici praestare proclive. Debet vero qualibet septima<pb type="VIII_1" n="32"/>na nova charta attigi priore demta, et horologium<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>horologium</term>
						</index> readduci <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">cum linea serrata</lem>
						<rdg wit="#L" cause="addition"><add>cum linea serrata</add> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">erg. L</hi></note></rdg>
						</app> seu reconstitui. <app type="Bfootnote">
						<lem type="main">Idque</lem>
						<note type="lemma-abbrev">reconstitui.</note>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="1"> Ita </rdg>
						<rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Idque <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg>
						</app> ne tempore minus congruo fiat, illud horologium<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>horologium</term>
						</index> simul horas sonet, aut si non placet, saltem tempore decursus prope finem insolite strepat. Et machina sit locata prope compas<index indexName="Sachverzeichnis">
						<term>Kompass</term>
						</index>, ne oblivione transmittatur.</p>
